text: Chaosphere is the third album by Swedish metal band Meshuggah. It was released on November 9 1998 by Nuclear Blast, the band's record label. It is the band's only album with bassist Gustaf Hielm. The band made a music video for the song "New Millenium Cyanide Christ". == Track listing == Category:Meshuggah albums Category:Nuclear Blast albums
title: Chaosphere
